    "custom_liquid_rQRi84": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Custom Liquid",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": true,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": true,
        "liquid": "<div class=\"why-fail-section\">\n  <div class=\"why-fail-header\">\n    <h2 class=\"why-fail-title\">You Didn't Stop Feeling Beautiful.<br>Your Closet Just Stopped Helping.</h2>\n    <p class=\"why-fail-sub\">Every summer dress you own has the same problem. Here's why none of them made the cut.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"why-fail-card\">\n    <div class=\"why-fail-card-title\">\n      <span class=\"why-x\">✕</span>\n      <strong>Bodycon and fitted dresses</strong>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"why-fail-card-body\">Looks great for the first twenty minutes. Then you eat, sit down, or breathe. You spend the rest of the night pulling it away from your stomach.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"why-fail-card\">\n    <div class=\"why-fail-card-title\">\n      <span class=\"why-x\">✕</span>\n      <strong>Loose maxi dresses</strong>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"why-fail-card-body\">Comfortable, sure. But shapeless. You look like you gave up getting dressed. The word you're thinking of is \"tent.\"</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"why-fail-card\">\n    <div class=\"why-fail-card-title\">\n      <span class=\"why-x\">✕</span>\n      <strong>Sundresses</strong>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"why-fail-card-body\">Cute until you stand in front of a window and realize everyone can see through it. And good luck finding one that works without a strapless bra.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"why-fail-card\">\n    <div class=\"why-fail-card-title\">\n      <span class=\"why-x\">✕</span>\n      <strong>Loungewear and pajamas</strong>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"why-fail-card-body\">The most comfortable thing you own, and the one thing you'd never leave the house in. You end up feeling invisible in your own kitchen.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"why-fail-card why-fail-card--solution\">\n    <div class=\"why-fail-card-title\">\n      <span class=\"why-check\">✓</span>\n      <strong>ELORYA · The Adjustable Back Dress</strong>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"why-fail-card-body\">Nothing touches your stomach. Not see-through, even in direct sunlight. The back adjusts from closed to open so you set the vibe yourself. Light enough to sleep in. Put-together enough for dinner. One dress from the kitchen to the coast.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.why-fail-section {\n  background: #f9f5f2;\n  padding: 40px 20px;\n  max-width: 680px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n.why-fail-header {\n  text-align: center;\n  margin-bottom: 28px;\n}\n.why-fail-title {\n  font-size: clamp(22px, 5vw, 30px);\n  font-weight: 800;\n  color: #1a1a1a;\n  line-height: 1.25;\n  margin-bottom: 14px;\n}\n.why-fail-sub {\n  font-size: 15px;\n  color: #777;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n  max-width: 520px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n.why-fail-card {\n  background: #ffffff;\n  border-radius: 14px;\n  padding: 20px 20px;\n  margin-bottom: 12px;\n  box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\n}\n.why-fail-card--solution {\n  background: #fdf6f3;\n  border: 2px solid #C4614A;\n}\n.why-fail-card-title {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 10px;\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n.why-fail-card-title strong {\n  font-size: 17px;\n  color: #1a1a1a;\n}\n.why-x {\n  color: #C4614A;\n  font-size: 18px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  line-height: 1;\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n.why-check {\n  color: #2e7d32;\n  font-size: 20px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  line-height: 1;\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n.why-fail-card-body {\n  font-size: 14px;\n  color: #555;\n  line-height: 1.65;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n@media (max-width: 480px) {\n  .why-fail-section { padding: 32px 16px; }\n  .why-fail-card { padding: 16px; }\n}\n</style>",
        "background": "",
        "background_gradient": "",
        "text_color": ""
      }
    },
    "custom_liquid_xTrrbw": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "disabled": true,
      "name": "Custom Liquid",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": true,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": true,
        "liquid": "<div class=\"expect-section\">\n\n  <h2 class=\"expect-title\">What To Expect</h2>\n\n  <div class=\"expect-card\">\n    <p class=\"expect-tag\">DAY 1</p>\n    <h3 class=\"expect-card-title\">Immediate relief</h3>\n    <p class=\"expect-card-body\">No wire digging into your ribs. No pressure points. Your shoulders drop and the all-day adjusting finally stops.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"expect-card\">\n    <p class=\"expect-tag\">WEEK 1–2</p>\n    <h3 class=\"expect-card-title\">You stop thinking about it</h3>\n    <p class=\"expect-card-body\">The CradleBand™ carries the weight from below — so your neck and shoulders do nothing. You get to 4pm and realize you haven't touched your bra once.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"expect-card\">\n    <p class=\"expect-tag\">WEEK 3–4</p>\n    <h3 class=\"expect-card-title\">Your clothes fit differently</h3>\n    <p class=\"expect-card-body\">Natural lift, natural separation. The tops you stopped wearing start coming back out of the closet.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"expect-card\">\n    <p class=\"expect-tag\">MONTH 2+</p>\n    <h3 class=\"expect-card-title\">You can't go back</h3>\n    <p class=\"expect-card-body\">Women tell us the same thing: they tried wearing their old bra for a day just to check. They sent it back within the hour.</p>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.expect-section {\n  background: #ffffff;\n  padding: 40px 20px;\n  max-width: 680px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n\n.expect-title {\n  font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 32px);\n  font-weight: 800;\n  color: #1a1a1a;\n  text-align: center;\n  margin-bottom: 28px;\n}\n\n.expect-card {\n  background: #f9f5f2;\n  border-radius: 14px;\n  padding: 24px 22px;\n  margin-bottom: 14px;\n}\n\n.expect-tag {\n  font-size: 12px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #C4614A;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n}\n\n.expect-card-title {\n  font-size: 20px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #1a1a1a;\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n  line-height: 1.3;\n}\n\n.expect-card-body {\n  font-size: 14px;\n  color: #666;\n  line-height: 1.65;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 480px) {\n  .expect-section { padding: 32px 16px; }\n  .expect-card { padding: 18px 16px; }\n}\n</style>",
        "background": "",
        "background_gradient": "",
        "text_color": ""
      }
