    "custom_liquid_hNKzgj": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Custom Liquid",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": true,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": true,
        "liquid": "<div class=\"reviews-section\">\n\n  <div class=\"reviews-header\">\n    <h2 class=\"reviews-title\">What Women Are Saying</h2>\n    <div class=\"reviews-rating\">\n      <span class=\"reviews-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n      <span class=\"reviews-count\">4.8 · 4,300+ Verified Reviews</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"reviews-slider\" id=\"reviewsSlider\">\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0795/2754/3033/files/426b24b2c2d4a4bbcaad34c3a36a40ba_430x.jpg?v=1784339819\" alt=\"Customer review\" class=\"review-img\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      <div class=\"review-body\">\n        <div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">\"5'7\", ordered a Medium in the khaki. I put it on after my shower just to try it. Never took it off. Made dinner in it, ran to CVS in it, watched TV in it. My husband asked me twice if I was going somewhere. I was going to the couch. Already ordered the black.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"review-footer\">\n          <strong class=\"review-name\">Danielle R.</strong>\n          <span class=\"review-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</span>\n          <span class=\"review-product\">Adjustable Back Dress · Khaki · Size M</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0795/2754/3033/files/713upueNRmL._SL300_430x.jpg?v=1784339819\" alt=\"Customer review\" class=\"review-img\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      <div class=\"review-body\">\n        <div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">\"I'm a size 8 and I was so worried it would look like a nightgown on me. It doesn't. The light blue is gorgeous and the back is the whole point. I adjust it closed when I go out and open it up at home. My boyfriend literally stopped talking mid-sentence the first time I wore it. Worth every penny.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"review-footer\">\n          <strong class=\"review-name\">Megan L.</strong>\n          <span class=\"review-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</span>\n          <span class=\"review-product\">Adjustable Back Dress · Sky Blue · Size S</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0795/2754/3033/files/16390e65c23b88c92324eaa14fbf0798_430x.jpg?v=1784339819\" alt=\"Customer review\" class=\"review-img\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      <div class=\"review-body\">\n        <div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">\"Wore this to a hotel dinner and got three compliments from strangers. Three. I had no makeup on, my hair was still wet from the pool, and I was barefoot in sandals. The black is not see-through at all, I checked in every mirror I could find. This is the only dress I packed for a five day trip and I regret nothing.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"review-footer\">\n          <strong class=\"review-name\">Nicole S.</strong>\n          <span class=\"review-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</span>\n          <span class=\"review-product\">Adjustable Back Dress · Black · Size S</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0795/2754/3033/files/2f4359ce0a7e0a4dceee1fe0e5773f67_430x.jpg?v=1784339819\" alt=\"Customer review\" class=\"review-img\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      <div class=\"review-body\">\n        <div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">\"5'3\" and I got the short version. Finally a dress that doesn't drag on the floor or make me look like I'm drowning in fabric. It hits right below my knee which is perfect. Nothing touches my stomach, I can eat a full meal and nobody can tell. I've worn it four days out of the last seven. No shame.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"review-footer\">\n          <strong class=\"review-name\">Ashley K.</strong>\n          <span class=\"review-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</span>\n          <span class=\"review-product\">Adjustable Back Dress · Black · Size M (Short)</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0795/2754/3033/files/fc3665e59b4a7a734fad457de8e5f8a7_430x.jpg?v=1784339819\" alt=\"Customer review\" class=\"review-img\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      <div class=\"review-body\">\n        <div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">\"I'm a 12 and I was terrified this would make me look bigger. It doesn't. The fabric falls straight from the bust and just floats over everything else. My back looks amazing in it and my stomach is completely free. I haven't sucked in once this entire week. That alone is worth the price.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"review-footer\">\n          <strong class=\"review-name\">Rachel M.</strong>\n          <span class=\"review-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</span>\n          <span class=\"review-product\">Adjustable Back Dress · Black · Size L (Short)</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0795/2754/3033/files/71bZSoU9etL._SL300_430x.jpg?v=1784339819\" alt=\"Customer review\" class=\"review-img\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      <div class=\"review-body\">\n        <div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">\"Size 20, 5'6\". I almost didn't order because every dress like this only shows size 4 models and I figured it would look completely different on me. It doesn't. It's loose in all the right places, the straps don't dig, and the back actually looks beautiful on a bigger body. I cried a little. Ordering two more colors.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"review-footer\">\n          <strong class=\"review-name\">Sandra J.</strong>\n          <span class=\"review-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</span>\n          <span class=\"review-product\">Adjustable Back Dress · Black · Size XXL</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"reviews-dots\" id=\"reviewsDots\"></div>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.reviews-section {\n  background: #ffffff;\n  padding: 40px 0 32px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n.reviews-header {\n  text-align: center;\n  padding: 0 20px;\n  margin-bottom: 24px;\n}\n.reviews-title {\n  font-size: clamp(26px, 5vw, 40px);\n  font-weight: 800;\n  color: #1a1a1a;\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n}\n.reviews-rating {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  gap: 10px;\n}\n.reviews-stars {\n  color: #C4614A;\n  font-size: 20px;\n  letter-spacing: 2px;\n}\n.reviews-count {\n  font-size: 14px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  color: #555;\n}\n.reviews-slider {\n  display: flex;\n  overflow-x: auto;\n  scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;\n  -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n  scroll-behavior: smooth;\n  scrollbar-width: none;\n  padding: 0 0 8px 0;\n}\n.reviews-slider::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }\n.reviews-slider::before,\n.reviews-slider::after {\n  content: '';\n  flex: 0 0 calc((100% - min(88vw, 480px)) / 2);\n}\n.review-card {\n  flex: 0 0 min(88vw, 480px);\n  scroll-snap-align: center;\n  background: #ffffff;\n  border: 1px solid #ede8e3;\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\n  margin: 0 8px;\n}\n.review-img {\n  width: 100%;\n  aspect-ratio: 4/4;\n  object-fit: cover;\n  object-position: top;\n  display: block;\n}\n.review-body {\n  padding: 20px;\n}\n.review-stars {\n  color: #C4614A;\n  font-size: 18px;\n  letter-spacing: 2px;\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n.review-text {\n  font-size: 14px;\n  font-style: italic;\n  color: #444;\n  line-height: 1.7;\n  margin-bottom: 14px;\n}\n.review-footer {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 6px;\n  border-top: 1px solid #f0ebe6;\n  padding-top: 12px;\n}\n.review-name {\n  font-size: 13px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #1a1a1a;\n}\n.review-verified {\n  font-size: 12px;\n  color: #2e7d32;\n  font-weight: 600;\n}\n.review-product {\n  font-size: 11px;\n  color: #aaa;\n  width: 100%;\n  margin-top: 2px;\n}\n.reviews-dots {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n  gap: 6px;\n  margin-top: 16px;\n  padding: 0 20px;\n}\n.reviews-dot {\n  width: 8px;\n  height: 8px;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  background: #ddd;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;\n  border: none;\n  padding: 0;\n}\n.reviews-dot.active {\n  background: #C4614A;\n  transform: scale(1.2);\n}\n</style>\n\n<script>\n(function() {\n  var slider = document.getElementById('reviewsSlider');\n  var dotsContainer = document.getElementById('reviewsDots');\n  var cards = slider.querySelectorAll('.review-card');\n  var dots = [];\n\n  cards.forEach(function(_, i) {\n    var dot = document.createElement('button');\n    dot.className = 'reviews-dot' + (i === 0 ? ' active' : '');\n    dot.setAttribute('aria-label', 'Review ' + (i + 1));\n    dot.addEventListener('click', function() {\n      var card = cards[i];\n      var sliderCenter = slider.offsetWidth / 2;\n      var cardCenter = card.offsetLeft + card.offsetWidth / 2;\n      slider.scrollTo({ left: cardCenter - sliderCenter, behavior: 'smooth' });\n    });\n    dotsContainer.appendChild(dot);\n    dots.push(dot);\n  });\n\n  slider.addEventListener('scroll', function() {\n    var sliderCenter = slider.scrollLeft + slider.offsetWidth / 2;\n    var closest = 0;\n    var minDist = Infinity;\n    cards.forEach(function(card, i) {\n      var dist = Math.abs(card.offsetLeft + card.offsetWidth / 2 - sliderCenter);\n      if (dist < minDist) { minDist = dist; closest = i; }\n    });\n    dots.forEach(function(d, i) {\n      d.classList.toggle('active', i === closest);\n    });\n  });\n})();\n</script>",
        "background": "",
        "background_gradient": "",
        "text_color": ""
      }
    },
    "custom_liquid_YynY3r": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Custom Liquid",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": true,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": true,
        "liquid": "<div class=\"faq-section\">\n  <h2 class=\"faq-title\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"faq-question\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      How adjustable is the open back?\n      <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n      <p>The back can be adjusted depending on how much coverage you want. Wear it slightly more closed when you're heading out, or loosen it for a deeper, more open-back look at home, on vacation, or by the beach.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"faq-question\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      Can I wear a bra with this dress?\n      <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n      <p>Because of the low open back, a standard bra may be visible. Depending on the support you prefer, you can wear it braless or pair it with nipple covers, adhesive cups, or another low-back solution. The adjustable straps also let you personalize the fit around your bust.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"faq-question\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      Should I choose the Short or Long length?\n      <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n      <p>Choose Short for an easy, playful everyday look, or Long for more coverage and a relaxed maxi-dress feel. Your height will affect where each version falls, so check the measurements in our size guide before ordering.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"faq-question\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      I'm between two sizes. Which one should I choose?\n      <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n      <p>The Caress™ Dress is intentionally cut loose and flowy, so we generally recommend choosing your usual size. If you're between sizes, choose the smaller size for a slightly closer fit or the larger size for extra drape and room.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"faq-question\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      Is it only a lounge dress, or can I wear it out?\n      <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n      <p>It's designed for both. Wear it barefoot around the house, over a swimsuit at the beach, or dress it up with sandals, jewelry, and a bag for errands, lunch, vacation dinners, and casual summer plans.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"faq-question\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      Can I adjust the straps and back separately?\n      <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n      <p>Yes. The shoulder straps help you adjust how the dress sits at the front, while the back adjustment lets you control the depth and openness of the back. This makes it easier to personalize both the fit and the amount of coverage.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"faq-question\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      How should I wash and care for it?\n      <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n      <p>Always follow the instructions on the garment care label. For best results, wash it gently in cold water with similar colors and let it air-dry. Avoid high heat, as it may affect the shape and softness of the fabric.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"faq-question\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      What if the size or length isn't right?\n      <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n      <p>Your order is protected by our 30-Day ELORYA Guarantee. If the size or length isn't right for you, you can request a return or exchange within 30 days, provided the dress meets the conditions listed in our return policy.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.faq-section {\n  background: #ffffff;\n  padding: 40px 20px;\n  max-width: 680px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n\n.faq-title {\n  font-size: clamp(22px, 5vw, 30px);\n  font-weight: 800;\n  color: #1a1a1a;\n  text-align: center;\n  margin-bottom: 28px;\n}\n\n.faq-item {\n  background: #ffffff;\n  border: 1px solid #ede8e3;\n  border-radius: 14px;\n  margin-bottom: 12px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.faq-question {\n  width: 100%;\n  background: none;\n  border: none;\n  padding: 20px 20px;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 16px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  text-align: left;\n  font-size: 15px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #1a1a1a;\n  line-height: 1.4;\n}\n\n.faq-question:hover { background: #fdf8f5; }\n\n.faq-icon {\n  color: #C4614A;\n  font-size: 22px;\n  font-weight: 400;\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n  transition: transform 0.25s ease;\n  line-height: 1;\n}\n\n.faq-question[aria-expanded=\"true\"] .faq-icon {\n  transform: rotate(45deg);\n}\n\n.faq-answer {\n  display: none;\n  padding: 0 20px 20px;\n}\n\n.faq-answer.open { display: block; }\n\n.faq-answer p {\n  font-size: 14px;\n  color: #666;\n  line-height: 1.7;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 480px) {\n  .faq-section { padding: 32px 16px; }\n  .faq-question { font-size: 14px; padding: 16px; }\n  .faq-answer { padding: 0 16px 16px; }\n}\n</style>\n\n<script>\ndocument.querySelectorAll('.faq-question').forEach(function(btn) {\n  btn.addEventListener('click', function() {\n    var expanded = this.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';\n\n    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question').forEach(function(b) {\n      b.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');\n      b.nextElementSibling.classList.remove('open');\n    });\n\n    if (!expanded) {\n      this.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');\n      this.nextElementSibling.classList.add('open');\n    }\n  });\n});\n</script>",
        "background": "",
        "background_gradient": "",
        "text_color": ""
      }
    },
