            "author": "",
            "title": "01-28-2026 · Michael T",
            "content": "<p>Been wearing these for 3 weeks now in Chicago. Walk my dog twice a day, rain or snow. My old Columbias would leave my feet frozen after 20 minutes. These? Warm the entire walk. The wide toe box is a game-changer - no more cramped toes. Worth every penny.</p>"
